{
  "defaultAction": "SCMP_ACT_ERRNO",
  "defaultErrnoRet": 1,
  "comment": "Docker default + CLONE_NEWUSER allowed. No io_uring (io_uring_setup/enter/register removed — the io_* entries are POSIX AIO, a different subsystem). No chroot, no pivot_root. mount/umount allowed for control plane bind mounts. Per-worker seccomp blocks clone(CLONE_NEWUSER), clone3, unshare, setns, mount, umount2 for agent processes.",
